<h2 style="text-align: center">DESIGN OF SOLUTIONS</h2>

<p>This can be done by the following ways / steps: - 

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Generating solution options;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Overcoming blocks in thinking;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Generative and lateral thinking;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Using criteria (social, political, ecological, technological, economic) to rank and prioritise solution ideas;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Check solutions for economic, social and technical viability;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Collation of solution into coherent plans;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Planning sequence and cost. 
